  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + Rigor Declaration">"🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL — New AI memory service; LLM-backed; budget-critical."</step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">Read TASK-INDEX; confirm 053 complete.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Gather Resources">Read PlaybookChatContextProvider + chat-architecture + AI-ARCHITECTURE memory sections.</step>
    <step order="3" name="Author Interface + Implementation">Create `ISummarizationCompressionService` + `SummarizationCompressionService` in `Services/Ai/Memory/`.</step>
    <step order="4" name="Implement Compression Logic">Sliding window detection; oldest M turns → GPT-4o-mini call → compressed summary; persist to Cosmos `sessions` container.</step>
    <step order="5" name="Wire into Provider">Wire into `PlaybookChatContextProvider` at the budget-management point; do NOT modify its public signature.</step>
    <step order="6" name="Register in Module">ADR-010 module pattern.</step>
    <step order="7" name="Tests">Unit tests: compression triggers at threshold; summary persisted; reuse on subsequent invocation; budget cap enforced.</step>
    <step order="8" name="Publish-Size + CVE">dotnet publish + vulnerable check.</step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality Gates (FULL)">code-review + adr-check (ADR-010/013/014/015/029).</step>
